name: N6 nuclear power plant
description:
N6 nuclear power plant
The n6 is the sixth generation nuclear power plant in Area 51.
The fuel produced by the power plant is used for city lighting, anti-aircraft systems and water purification.
Due to the sensitivity of n6, we build it in the mountains so that they are not easily recognizable and are far from our people in case of an accident.
In the recent war in Area 51, nuclear power plants operated in complete safety with the sacrifice of our generals.
Engineer Yuri, a nuclear physicist, is preparing a n6 map of the seventh generation of nuclear power plants.
